    <item>
      <title>Investcorp 聘请资深人士 Lopez-Cruz 担任全球 PE 主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/investcorp-brings-back-veteran-lopez-cruz-as-global-head-of-pe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Investcorp Holdings 表示，丹尼尔·洛佩兹-克鲁兹 (Daniel Lopez-Cruz) 将重新加入中东最大的另类资产管理公司，担任私募股权全球主管，就在一年多前，他离开这家公司成立了一家咨询公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/investcorp-brings-back-veteran-lopez-cruz-as-global-head-of-pe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 07:49:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贷款紧缩导致泰国 2024 年汽车销量下降 26%，实现“亚洲底特律”目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/thailand-s-detroit-of-asia-nickname-hit-as-car-sales-fall-26-on-loan-squeeze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国国内汽车销量跌至 14 年来的最低水平，损害了其作为“亚洲底特律”的声誉，因为银行贷款审批收紧和家庭债务高企抑制了汽车需​​求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/thailand-s-detroit-of-asia-nickname-hit-as-car-sales-fall-26-on-loan-squeeze</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 07:21:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ING 出售俄罗斯业务将损失 7 亿欧元利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/ing-to-take-700-million-profit-hit-to-sell-russian-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰国际集团（ING Groep NV）同意以未公开的价格出售其俄罗斯业务，并在其入侵乌克兰三年后退出俄罗斯，导致其利润损失 7 亿欧元（7.3 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/ing-to-take-700-million-profit-hit-to-sell-russian-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 07:04:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港费用下降反映银行业竞争加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/banks-compete-for-catl-listing-big-china-ipos-in-hong-kong-with-cheap-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宁德时代科技股份有限公司即将进行大规模上市，可能募资逾 50 亿美元，这类交易可以为香港等低迷的市场注入急需的活力。但这很快就成为华尔街银行的头疼事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/banks-compete-for-catl-listing-big-china-ipos-in-hong-kong-with-cheap-fees</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 07:03:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税和 DeepSeek 波动令亚洲各地货币交易员困惑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/asia-hedge-funds-stumped-on-tariff-deepseek-currency-whiplash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场参与者表示，关税风险上升、科技领域可能出现的“斯普尼克时刻”以及假期临近，让亚洲各地的对冲基金和其他货币交易商不知道该下什么赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/asia-hedge-funds-stumped-on-tariff-deepseek-currency-whiplash</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 06:46:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚抗议停止东部主要港口的石油运输</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/libya-s-ras-lanuf-es-sider-ports-ordered-to-stop-oil-loadings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于抗议活动阻碍了利比亚这个欧佩克成员国约三分之一的原油出口，利比亚两个主要港口的石油装载陷入停滞，这提醒人们，这个北非国家持续的紧张局势给全球供应带来了风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/libya-s-ras-lanuf-es-sider-ports-ordered-to-stop-oil-loadings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 05:12:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
