    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银即将与印度财富管理公司 360 One 达成协议以促进增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/ubs-nears-deal-with-india-wealth-firm-360-one-for-growth-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团 (UBS Group AG) 正在与印度 360 One WAM Ltd. 进行深入谈判，该交易将增强该瑞士银行在该国蓬勃发展的财富市场的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/ubs-nears-deal-with-india-wealth-firm-360-one-for-growth-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 02:57:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
